HEADWORD: Admix
<hw>Ad*mix"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>ad-</ets> + <ets>mix</ets>: cf. L. <ets>admixtus</ets>, p. p. of
<ets>admiscere</ets>. See <er>Mix</er>.]</ety> <def>To mingle with
something else; to mix.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

